st had milk and whiskey. .. also, if ur flight is not until later and u have to check out, u can ask the bell boys in front to keep your bags for you and you can frolick some more around town without worrying about bags. just make sure to tip the bellboys :) thanks tuscany. my first vegas experence was truly epic!! i would come back definitely.	
