 is a great casino. Cocktail waitresses were really attentive and ffriendly, so were the waitresses in Marilyns Cafe, especially Maureen, she was great. All the guys on the bell desk were great, especially once they got to know us.Even though the hotel suites were running at full capacity most of the time we were there it was never crowded. We all had a fabulous holiday, and will definitely stay at the Tuscany Suites when we visit again next year. Cant wait!!!	
